locality: Oman: Oman, Dhofar: Jabal Qara, road between Salalah and Thumrit, 100 m S of the first military post, succulent-rich rocky ridge with dominating Euphorbia balsamifera shrubs, alt. 775 m, 17°17'N, 54°05'E. Alt.: 775 m. 5.10.1998, Leg.: P. Hein & N. Kilian PH 5341.

Yemen: Gov. Al-Mahra. Northern Fartak Mts, W flank of J. Karmoum. Oman: Oman, Dhofar: SE facing slopes of the Jabal Qara along the track between Raysut and Qaftawt, Anogeissus dhofarica - Commiphora woodland, alt. 300-350 m, 17°03'N, 53°54'E. Slopes with strongly degraded woodland and dense grassland. Alt.: 300-350 m. 3.10.1998, Leg.: P. Hein & N. Kilian PH 5167a.
